                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS WILLIAMS</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">further</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to having been before con<lb></lb>victed, in April</hi>, 1862, <hi rend="italic">in the name of Thomas Fowler.</hi>
               </p>
